					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Spoiler tag if you haven't beaten TMNT:  Fall of the Footclan (GB) and Donkey Kong Country 2 (SNES).<br /><br />I used to be scared of endings where the bad guy laughs at you, like the shot of Krang at the end of TMNT:  Fall of the Footclan (Also the ending of the Batman:TAS episode Demon's Quest).  DKC2 had a menacing atmosphere in its 102% end sequence.<br /><br />Super Metroid's elevator/item/defeated boss rooms always freaked me out.  So did the ghost house in Mario 64 (Don't play Resident Evil, I was told back then).</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

